Simple command line utility to create bittorrent metainfo files
	
mktorrent is a text-based utility to create bittorrent metainfo files
used by trackers and torrent clients. it can create metainfo files for single
files or complete directories in a fast way.

it also supports:

 - multiple trackers
 - embed custom comments into the file
 - dissalow dht and peer exchange
 - support for multi-threaded hashing